OL,4,CCovid: Isolation rules loosened for
OL,5,Ccritical workers
OL,6, Some fully vaccinated people in
OL,7, critical roles in England will be able
OL,8, to continue working even if told to
OL,9, self-isolate after being in close
OL,10, contact with someone who has Covid.
OL,12,FInstead those eligible - including NHS
OL,13,Fand care staff - will be able to take
OL,14,Fdaily tests, the government said.
OL,16,FA list of critical workers is due to be
OL,17,Fpublished, but the PM said it included
OL,18,Ffood, utility and border staff.
OL,20,FIt follows mounting criticism of the
OL,21,Fimpact of self-isolation on industry.
